body:
The "pixel quadruplets by triplet propagation" seeding algorithm was superseded by Cellular Automaton in the spring. We don't foresee "going back", so this PR removes the tracking customization with `trackingPhase1QuadProp` era, the special workflows exercising that tracking, and the algorithm code.

Tested in CMSSW_10_0_X_2017-12-05-1100, no changes expected.

@VinInn
